data.description: **HIGHLY MOTIVATED SELLERS** LAKE HOME and BOATER'S PARADISE - If you're dreaming of a home near Lake Texoma this adorable brick home in Tanglewood Resort may be the perfect solution.Tanglewood Resort, Highport Marina & Island Bar & Grill are just a stone's throw away, offering convenient access to the lake for your boating lifestyle. This split-level home teases all your senses as soon as you enter through the doors. The first level offers a spacious living area open to the kitchen & dining, 3 bedrooms, 2 baths with doors leading to a large deck & a spacious tree-shaded backyard. The lower basement level includes a Flex room with a full bath. When not boating on the lake, you'll enjoy the serenity of a lake view & gorgeous sunsets from the front covered deck. The oversized covered parking area allows for plenty of parking for the RV, Boat and other lake toys. Come see why families love living on Lake Texoma.
